Package dev.yangsijun.gauth.userinfo

Interface GAuthUserService<R extends GAuthAuthorizationRequest,U extends GAuthUser>

Type Parameters:
R - The type of GAuth Authorization Request
U - The type of GAuth User
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultGAuthUserService
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface GAuthUserService<R extends GAuthAuthorizationRequest,U extends GAuthUser>
An interface for loading GAuth users based on GAuth Authorization Requests. The implementation is responsible for retrieving user information from GAuth and constructing instances of GAuthUser.
Since:
2.0.0

Yang Sijun
